onar a Ampharos en combate.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/7/", "name": "es"}}, {"text": "Erhöht den Angriff und den Spezial-Angriff des\nTrägers stark, wenn er von einer sehr effektiven\nAttacke getroffen wird.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/6/", "name": "de"}}, {"text": "Objet à tenir. Augmente beaucoup l’Attaque et\nl’Attaque Spéciale du Pokémon lorsqu’il reçoit\nun coup d’un type auquel il est vulnérable.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/5/", "name": "fr"}}, {"text": "약점을 공격당했을 때\n공격과 특수공격이\n각각 크게 올라간다.", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/3/", "name": "ko"}}, {"text": "じゃくてんを　つかれたとき\nこうげきと　とくこうが\nそれぞれ　ぐーんと　あがる。", "version_group": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/version-group/15/", "name": "x-y"}, "language": {"url": "http://pokeapi.co/api/v2/language/1/", "name": "ja"}}], "sprites": {"default": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/items/weakness-policy.png"}, "machines": [], "fling_power": null}